{"tid":2198652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分咗手，佢話想同我繼續做朋友","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T14:43:49.000Z","uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26dab8c81f64b476dd6d13f4166310a5dbb5cec7","tid":2198652,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"早一排分咗手，佢話希望可以同我做朋友，保持聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n我問過佢點解，佢話因為唔想好似一分開就完全消失咗，驚我會好難過。<br />\n<br />\n但前幾日發現佢已經同另一個人一齊。我同佢講都係唔好做朋友啦，佢又唔肯。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知而家維持朋友嘅關係係咪好事，定係無限延伸痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e5ad444dbd035a11cf781988c4b476dc3586cb","tid":2198652,"uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"夠鐘食藥啦，道友"},{"pid":"17d903ffa3bc1d37405bb90a9304c017384d8978","tid":2198652,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"做炮友囉"},{"pid":"02754569ea1a6f0fcc2f0773965d4ba8a18f5def","tid":2198652,"uid":367354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:29:12.000Z","msg":"J痕就揾你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想做免費雞就快啲走啦"},{"pid":"3325bfe1d0fe7b0b79d1f59ea9b3898e92d1f955","tid":2198652,"uid":238862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"又多一pair分手 開心死"},{"pid":"236f3ad34e85199d231413da27a841e0c5f1c225","tid":2198652,"uid":144156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再見亦是炮友"},{"pid":"6940a38f8f4a92d4a91c82d99438ca2aa9a5bda4","tid":2198652,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20e5ad444dbd035a11cf781988c4b476dc3586cb","tid":2198652,"uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy